ques.p: To ask the Secretary of State for Work and Pensions when he plans to answer the letters from the hon. Member for Edinburgh West of 22 September 2008 and 17 November 2008 on the case of the hon. Member's constituent, Joe Shepherd.

reply.p: A reply was sent to the hon. Member on 19 October 2008 in reply to his letter of 22 September 2008, and December 2008 in reply to his letter of 17 November 2008.
